#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:55
msgid "Each shortcut is assigned a default, which may be empty. The user can assign up to two custom shortcuts, known as primary and alternate shortcuts. Simply click on a \"Custom\" button and type the key combination you wish to assign to the shortcut. If the key combination is already in use for another shortcut, the dialog will prompt the user to resolve the conflict."
